data.description: Welcome to your nearly new home! Nestled in a well-kept community, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you drive in, you'll immediately appreciate the spaciousness of the large piece of land this home sits on.  Step inside to discover 4 generously sized bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a loft, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The open concept design seamlessly connects the inviting family room and kitchen, complete with a peninsula and spacious pantry.    Escape to the second-level master suite, boasting a walk-in closet and a master bath for your ultimate comfort. Additional features include granite countertops, LED lighting, LVP flooring in wet areas, and a Smart Home System, ensuring modern convenience throughout.    Outside, the leveled and private backyard offers the perfect retreat, with an invisible fence that opens to enjoyable serene surroundings.    Conveniently located just minutes from shopping and dining options, as well as easy access to Interstate I-475, this home provides the ideal combination of tranquility and accessibility.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule your tour today!
